Package: plotpy
Architecture: all
Depends: python (>= 2.4), gnuplot (>= 4.2), python-numpy (>= 1.0), python-scipy (>= 0.7), python-gtk2 (>= 2.0), python-gobject (>= 2.0), python-imaging, ipython, gfortran, gcc
Description: Program to plot measured data with Gnuplot. Provides a GUI interface, fitting and some other useful functionalities. Supports treatment for XRD, XRR, PND, PNR, SAS, GISAS scattering and other data and can be widened with plugins.
Replaces: plot-script